#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Usage"
msgstr "Napredna raba"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Line Options"
msgstr "Možnosti ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When running &appname; from the command line, there are several options for "
"opening data files. They may be seen by running <userinput>tellico --help</"
"userinput>. Diagnostic logging can also be enabled, which will make a <link "
"linkend=\"settings-help-menu\">menu item</link> to show the diagnostic log. "
"The <userinput>--logfile</userinput> option redirects the log to a file."
msgstr ""
"Ko izvajate &appname; v ukazni vrstici, obstaja več možnosti za odpiranje "
"podatkovnih datotek. Lahko jih vidite, če zaženete <userinput>tellico --"
"help</userinput>. Omogočeno je lahko tudi beleženje diagnostičnih dnevnikov, "
"kjer bo prikazan <link linkend=\"settings-help-menu\">menijski element</"
"link> za prikaz diagnostičnega dnevnika. Možnost <userinput>--logfile</"
"userinput> preusmeri dnevnik v datoteko."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: advanced.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Usage: tellico [options] [filename]\n"
"\n"
"Tellico - collection management software, free and simple\n"
"\n"
"Options:\n"
"  --nofile                  Do not reopen the last open file\n"
"  --bibtex                  Import &lt;filename&gt; as a bibtex file\n"
"  --mods                    Import &lt;filename&gt; as a MODS file\n"
"  --ris                     Import &lt;filename&gt; as a RIS file\n"
"  --pdf                     Import &lt;filename&gt; as a PDF file\n"
"  --log                     Log diagnostic output\n"
"  --logfile &lt;logfile&gt;       Write log output to &lt;filename&gt;\n"
"\n"
"Arguments:\n"
"  [filename]                File to open"
msgstr ""
"Raba: tellico [možnosti] [filename]\n"
"\n"
"Tellico - programska oprema za upravljanje zbirk - prosta in preprosta\n"
"\n"
"Možnosti:\n"
"  --nofile                  Ponovno ne odpiraj zadnje odprte datoteke\n"
"  --bibtex                  Uvoz &lt;filename&gt; kot datoteka bibtex\n"
"  --mods                    Uvoz &lt;filename&gt; kot datoteka MODS\n"
"  --ris                     Uvoz &lt;filename&gt; kot datoteka RIS\n"
"  --pdf                     Uvoz &lt;filename&gt; kot datoteka PDF\n"
" --log                     Izhod dnevnika diagnostike\n"
"  --logfile &lt;logfile&gt;       Piši izhod dnevnika v &lt;filename&gt;\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Argumenti:\n"
"  [filename]                Datoteka za odpiranje"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "&DBus; Interface"
msgstr "&DBus; Vmesnik"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&appname; has a minimal &DBus; interface, which can be useful for scripting "
"or interacting with a running application from the command-line. As with all "
"&DBus; calls, you need to specify the service you want to interface with, "
"and the particular interface. The name of the &DBus; service is "
"<constant>org.kde.tellico</constant>."
msgstr ""
"&appname; ima minimalen &DBus; vmesnik, ki je lahko uporaben za skriptiranje "
"ali interakcijo z delujočo aplikacijo iz ukazne vrstice. Kot pri vseh&DBus; "
"klicih morate določiti storitev, s katero želite vzpostaviti vmesnik,in "
"poseben vmesnik. Ime storitev &DBus; <constant>org.kde.tellico</constant>."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "&DBus; Commands"
msgstr "Ukazi &DBus;"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Two &DBus; primary objects are available in the tellico interface: "
"<constant>Tellico</constant> and <constant>Collections</constant>."
msgstr ""
"Dva primarna objekta &DBus; sta na razpolago v vmesniku tellico: "
"<constant>Tellico</constant> in <constant>Zbirke</constant>."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <constant>Tellico</constant> Object"
msgstr "<constant>Tellico</constant> Objekt"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The full list of &DBus; commands in the <constant>tellico</constant> object "
"is shown below:"
msgstr ""
"Poln seznam ukazov &DBus; v <constant>tellico</constant> objektu je prikazan "
"spodaj:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: advanced.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool importTellico(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool importBibtex(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool importMODS(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool importPDF(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool importRIS(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool exportXML(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"bool exportZip(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"bool exportBibtex(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"bool exportHTML(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"bool exportCSV(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"QList&lt;int&gt; selectedEntries()\n"
"QList&lt;int&gt; filteredEntries()\n"
"void openFile(QString file)\n"
"void setFilter(QString text)\n"
"bool showEntry(int id)"
msgstr ""
"bool importTellico(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool importBibtex(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool importMODS(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool importPDF(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool importRIS(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool exportXML(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"bool exportZip(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"bool exportBibtex(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"bool exportHTML(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"bool exportCSV(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"QList&lt;int&gt; selectedEntries()\n"
"QList&lt;int&gt; filteredEntries()\n"
"void openFile(QString file)\n"
"void setFilter(QString text)\n"
"bool showEntry(int id)"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the four import commands, the first argument is the file to import, and "
"the second is the import action. Three actions are available: "
"<emphasis>replace</emphasis>, <emphasis>append</emphasis>, and "
"<emphasis>merge</emphasis>. Four file formats are supported for importing: "
"Tellico &XML; files, Bibtex files, MODS files, and RIS files. Metadata from "
"<link linkend=\"importing-pdf\">&PDF;</link> files can also be imported."
msgstr ""
"Pri štirih ukazih za uvoz je prvi argument datoteka za uvoz, drugi pa "
"dejanje uvoza. Na voljo so tri dejanja: <emphasis>zamenjaj</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>dodaj</emphasis> in <emphasis>spoji</emphasis>. Za uvoz so podprti "
"štirje formati datotek: Tellico &XML; datoteke, datoteke Bibtex, datoteke "
"MODS in datoteke RIS. Metapodatke iz datotek <link linkend=\"importing-pdf"
"\">&PDF;</link> je tudi mogoče uvoziti."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For any of the commands to export text, a file name of <filename>--</"
"filename> will pipe to the standard output."
msgstr ""
"Za kateri koli od ukazov za izvoz besedila bo ime datoteke <filename>--</"
"filename> napeljalo na standardni izhod."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The current open collection in &appname; may be exported to a file, in "
"either Tellico &XML; format, Tellico ZIP format, Bibtex, &HTML;, or comma-"
"separated values (CSV). The export commands take an optional argument to "
"specify whether the collection should be limited to the current filter or "
"not."
msgstr ""
"Trenutna odprta zbirka v &appname; lahko izvozite v datoteko bodisi v "
"Tellico &XML; format Tellico ZIP, Bibtex, &HTML; ali vrednosti, ločene z "
"vejico (CSV). Ukazi za izvoz sprejmejo izbirni argument, s katerim določijo, "
"ali naj bo zbirka omejena na trenutni filter ali ne."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A list of the entry IDs currently selected or being filtered is able to "
"facilitate showing or updating entries in the view."
msgstr ""
"Seznam ID-jev vnosov, ki so trenutno izbrani ali filtrirani, lahko olajša "
"prikazovanje ali posodabljanje vnosov v pogledu."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A new data file may be opened by using the <command>openFile()</command> "
"command. The full path must be specified."
msgstr ""
"Novo podatkovno datoteko lahko odprete z ukazom <command>openFile()</"
"command>. Določiti je treba celotno pot."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A new filter may be set using the <command>setFilter()</command> command, "
"which is the equivalent of typing in the filter box in the main window."
msgstr ""
"Nov filter lahko nastavite z ukazom <command>setFilter()</command>, ki je "
"enakovreden vnašanju v polje filtra v glavnem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Given an entry ID, <command>showEntry()</command> will select that entry and "
"show the entry details in the main window."
msgstr ""
"Glede na ID vnosa bo <command>showEntry()</command> izbral ta vnos in "
"prikazal podrobnosti vnosa v glavnem oknu."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <constant>Collections</constant> Object"
msgstr "Objekt <constant>Zbirke</constant>"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The full list of &DBus; commands in the <constant>Collections</constant> "
"object is shown below:"
msgstr ""
"Celoten seznam &DBus; ukazov v objektu <constant>Zbirke</constant> je "
"prikazan spodaj:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: advanced.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int addEntry()\n"
"bool removeEntry(int entryID)\n"
"QStringList allValues(QString fieldName)\n"
"QStringList entryValues(int entryID, QString fieldName)\n"
"QStringList selectedBibtexKeys()\n"
"QString entryBibtexKey(int entryID)\n"
"bool setEntryValue(int entryID, QString fieldName, QString value)\n"
"bool addEntryValue(int entryID, QString fieldName, QString value)"
msgstr ""
"int addEntry()\n"
"bool removeEntry(int entryID)\n"
"QStringList allValues(QString fieldName)\n"
"QStringList entryValues(int entryID, QString fieldName)\n"
"QStringList selectedBibtexKeys()\n"
"QString entryBibtexKey(int entryID)\n"
"bool setEntryValue(int entryID, QString fieldName, QString value)\n"
"bool addEntryValue(int entryID, QString fieldName, QString value)"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A new empty entry may be created in the current collection using the "
"<command>addEntry()</command> command. The return value is the entry ID, "
"which can then be used to set the field values in the entry. An entry can be "
"deleted from the collection by calling <command>removeEntry()</command>."
msgstr ""
"Nov prazen vnos se lahko ustvari v trenutni zbirki z uporabo ukaza "
"<command>addEntry()</command>. Povratna vrednost je ID vnosa, ki jih lahko "
"nato uporabite za nastavitev vrednosti polj v vnosu. Vnos je lahkoizbrisani "
"iz zbirke s klicem <command>removeEntry()</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Calling <command>allValues()</command> using just a field name will return "
"all the values for that field for the currently selected entries. If no "
"entries are selected, the return list is empty. If an entry ID is included "
"in the command, the field values for that specific entry are returned."
msgstr ""
"Klic <command>allValues()</command> z uporabo samo imena polja bo vrnil vse "
"vrednosti za to polje za trenutno izbrane vnose. Če ni izbranih vnosov je "
"povratni seznam prazen. Če je vključen ID vnosa v ukazu so vrnjene vrednosti "
"polja za ta določen vnos."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the current collection is a bibliography, calling "
"<command>selectedBibtexKeys()</command> will return the Bibtex citation key "
"for all selected entries. The bibtexKey for a specific entry may be found by "
"using the <command>entryBibtexKey()</command> command."
msgstr ""
"Če je tekoča zbirka bibliografija, klic <command>selectedBibtexKeys()</"
"command> vrne ključ navedbe Bibtex za vse izbrane vnose. BibtexKey za "
"določen vnos lahko najdete v z uporabo ukaza <command>entryBibtexKey()</"
"command>."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entries can be edited directly with the &DBus; interface. Given an entry ID, "
"<command>setEntryValue()</command> will set the field value directly. To add "
"a value, without affecting the existing values, use "
"<command>addEntryValue()</command>. The new value gets appended to the end "
"of the existing list."
msgstr ""
"Vnose lahko urejate neposredno z &DBus; vmesnikom. Glede na vnosa ID, bo "
"<command>setEntryValue()</command> neposredno nastavil vrednost polja. Da bi "
"dodali vrednost, ne da bi to vplivalo na obstoječe vrednosti, uporabite "
"<command>addEntryValue()</command>. Nova vrednost se doda na konec "
"obstoječega seznama."

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "&DBus; Examples"
msgstr "&DBus; Primeri"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here are some examples for scripting &appname; using the &DBus; interface. "
"Note that the <command>qdbus</command> command may exist as <command>qdbus-"
"qt5</command> or something similar on your system."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je nekaj primerov za skript &appname; z uporabo vmesnika &DBus;. "
"Upoštevajte, da lahko na vašem sistemu ukaz <command>qdbus</command> obstaja "
"kot <command>qdbus-qt5</command> ali kaj podobnega."

#. Tag: screen
#: advanced.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Open a Bibtex file</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Tellico org.kde.tellico."
"importBibtex \"/home/robby/reference.bib\" \"replace\"</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>true</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Odpri datoteko Bibtex</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Tellico org.kde.tellico."
"importBibtex \"/home/robby/reference.bib\" \"replace\"</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>true</computeroutput>"

#. Tag: screen
#: advanced.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Export a Bibtex file</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Tellico org.kde.tellico."
"exportBibtex ~/documents/reference.bib</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>true</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Izvoz datoteke Bibtex file</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Tellico org.kde.tellico."
"exportBibtex ~/documents/reference.bib</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>true</computeroutput>"

#. Tag: screen
#: advanced.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Export a Bibtex file using the current filter</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Tellico org.kde.tellico."
"exportBibtex ~/documents/reference.bib true</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>true</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Izvoz datoteke Bibtex z uporabo trenutnega filtra</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Tellico org.kde.tellico."
"exportBibtex ~/documents/reference.bib true</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>true</computeroutput>"

#. Tag: screen
#: advanced.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Echo the citation key of the current selection</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Collections org.kde."
"tellico.selectedBibtexKeys</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>stephenson2004</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Odmev ključa navedbe trenutne izbire</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Collections org.kde."
"tellico.selectedBibtexKeys</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>stephenson2004</computeroutput>"

#. Tag: screen
#: advanced.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Add a new entry and set the title</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>myid=`qdbus org.kde.tellico /Collections org."
"kde.tellico.addEntry`</userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Collections org.kde."
"tellico.setEntryValue $myid title \"My New Book\"</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>true</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Dodaj nov vnos in nastavi naslov</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>myid=`qdbus org.kde.tellico /Collections org."
"kde.tellico.addEntry`</userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Collections org.kde."
"tellico.setEntryValue $myid title \"My New Book\"</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>true</computeroutput>"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Here are some examples for scripting &appname; using the &DBus; interface."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Tukaj je nekaj primerov za skript &appname; z uporabo &DBus; vmesnika."
